itunes:title: You Are Called to Become - Part 3
title: You Are Called to Become - Part 3
description: In this broadcast, Pastor Rick explains how your spiritual gifts were not given for your own benefit but for the benefit of others, just as other people were given gifts for your benefit. “There are different kinds of service, but we serve the same Lord” (1 Corinthians 12:5 NLT).
